{"ID":"20260609125745-k12bfi8","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609125745-k12bfi8","title":"2020年新高考Ⅱ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609125806-0jr8tie","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125806-0jr8tie","updated":"20260609125806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"风筝，是中国古人的一项重要发明,放风筝是一种人们喜闻乐见的传统活动。早期有关风筝的记载多与传递信息等军事活动有关。到唐代，风筝开始出现在文人诗歌中。宋代以后，逐渐演变成一种老少皆宜的玩具，而清明时节放风筝也成为一项普及的民俗活动。明代以后，风筝传播到世界各地，并深受各国人民喜爱。（      ），吸引着大批中外风筝专家、爱好者及游人前来观赏和竞技。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125806-i1rzhe8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125806-i1rzhe8","updated":"20260609125806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"早期的风筝制作十分简单，用竹篾做骨架，贴上素绢或白纸，结好线绳，便可放飞了。随着时间的推移，风筝的制作技艺不断炉火纯青，样式也逐渐丰富起来，从动物、植物、器具、文字，到人物、仙佛，不一而足，风筝于是有了很强的观赏性和艺术价值。有些风筝还安装了声响装置，如著名的“板鹞”风筝，通体安装笛哨，少则数十个，多则成百上千。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"放飞时百哨齐鸣，宛若空中交响乐，具有独特的魅力，大大增加了放风筝的趣味性。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125745-4l7ih5p","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125745-4l7ih5p","updated":"20260609125818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609125818-btuqoxt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125818-btuqoxt","updated":"20260609125818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．文段中加点的词语使用不当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609125818-gr23zh7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125818-gr23zh7","updated":"20260609125818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．喜闻乐见                                                                  B．老少皆宜"}]},{"ID":"20260609125818-y11a7ro","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125818-y11a7ro","updated":"20260609125818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．炉火纯青                                                                   D．不一而足"}]},{"ID":"20260609125818-k6qg48r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125818-k6qg48r","updated":"20260609125818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．下列填入文中括号内的语句，最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609125818-j0kj411","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125818-j0kj411","updated":"20260609125818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．自1984年开始，迄今已经连续举办了36届山东潍坊国际风筝节"}]},{"ID":"20260609125818-v9dz3ee","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125818-v9dz3ee","updated":"20260609125818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．自1984年开始，迄今已经连续举办了36届的山东潍坊国际风筝节"}]},{"ID":"20260609125818-ufq6o8v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125818-ufq6o8v","updated":"20260609125818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．山东潍坊自1984年开始迄今已经连续举办了36届国际风筝节"}]},{"ID":"20260609125818-sxp5kzd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125818-sxp5kzd","updated":"20260609125818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．山东潍坊自1984年开始迄今已经连续举办了36届的国际风筝节"}]},{"ID":"20260609125818-1juqj0n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125818-1juqj0n","updated":"20260609125818"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．比喻具有相似性，请据此对文中画横线的句子所用比喻进行简要分析。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125745-k5yocpk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125745-k5yocpk","updated":"20260609125828"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609125745-3bns6ps","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125745-3bns6ps","updated":"20260609125828"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．C    19．B    20．①句中把放飞风筝时百哨齐鸣的声音比作交响乐，体现了比喻的相似性；②放飞风筝时百哨齐鸣，交响乐由多人共同演奏，二者相似；③交响乐很有魅力，笛哨声也很有魅力，二者相似。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125745-m086a54","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609125745-m086a54","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-q9euff9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-q9euff9","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．本题考查正确使用成语的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-r4e8yqa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-r4e8yqa","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A项，喜闻乐见：喜欢听，乐意看。形容很受欢迎。符合语境。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-tcry5bw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-tcry5bw","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B项，老少皆宜：指老人和儿童都适宜，喻指适用的范围非常广。符合语境。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-p3mf7qh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-p3mf7qh","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C项，炉火纯青：比喻功夫达到了纯熟完美的境界。此处前面由“不断”修饰，而“完美”境界应该只有一个，因此该词不符合语境。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-yb76onw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-yb76onw","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D项，不一而足：同类的事物不止一个而是很多，无法列举齐全。符合语境。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-o6jsnyw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-o6jsnyw","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-ze7lecz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-ze7lecz","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．本题考查学生根据语境补写句子的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-zhu8zk6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-zhu8zk6","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“吸引……观赏和竞技”的主语应该是“国际风筝节”，CD两项主语是“山东潍坊”，与后句无法搭配，排除；"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-otnfrrd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-otnfrrd","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A项，“山东潍坊国际风筝节”作“举办”的宾语，无法同时作后句的主语，同时“已经连续”缺主语，排除。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-3l3ys24","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-3l3ys24","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-hzaqss2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-hzaqss2","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．本题考查赏析比喻修辞手法的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609125840-f83u8vj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609125840-f83u8vj","updated":"20260609125840"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题干明确要求要分析比喻的“相似性”，首先要找出本体和喻体，再分析其相似点；画线句把“百哨齐鸣”比喻成“空中交响乐”，首先是声音上具有相似性；无数风筝上的哨声争相鸣响，正宛如“交响乐”的多人演奏，声音交织，在乐声的特点上也具有相似性；“具有独特的魅力”，风筝的哨声和交响乐一样都具有独特的魅力，体现了二者的相似性。"}]}]}